title: The 3D dildo
description: The 3Dildo - Our first realistic dildo allows people to scale and print a dildo in the exact size they desire. Some people believe this is the reason that 3D printers will become popular. I agree. People with these devices will want to print all sorts of things and they will certainly want to avoid buying them in a store. Note, these photos show the dildo as it will print, with external support. You can easily remove the support and have just the dildo itself.
